reviews.review_text: Great show Night and day difference between this and 6/15. Most consistent 92 show i've heard so far.

5 bagger all the way.... A friend and I are working on a project where we are listening to every single show from the vincera. And looking for the highs as well as the Lowes. Analyzing and taking notes.

This is probably the best show of the summer tour so far, and there have been some good ones. But they come in to Charlotte Coliseum this night owning the venue, deliberate setlist, very intentional, and just rocking the crap out of the show from the very beginning. Also, the sound quality on these 92 shows is really really good and they're just fun to listen to these boards
